A. Audit principles
B. Audit decision factors
C. Audit evidence
D. Audit phases

15. Which phase involves defining scope, objectives, and checklist?
A. Execution
B. Planning
C. Reporting
D. Follow-up

16. Independence of internal audit team can be ensured by:
A. Reporting to IT head
B. Reporting to senior management or audit committee
C. Reporting to system admins
D. Reporting to vendors

17. Which principle ensures audit findings are protected from disclosure?
A. Integrity
B. Confidentiality
C. Independence
D. Objectivity

