A. Programming
B. Communication
C. Network design
D. Cryptography

19. Compliance failure can result in:
A. Only technical issues
B. Legal penalties and reputational damage
C. Improved productivity
D. Reduced audits

20. Which audit phase validates corrective actions?
A. Planning
B. Reporting
C. Follow-up
D. Evidence collection

